58
00:04:22,310 --> 00:04:24,331
[SPEAKER_04]: thing at the library.

59
00:04:24,351 --> 00:04:28,513
[SPEAKER_04]: And it's really around getting people prepared for the winter.

60
00:04:28,533 --> 00:04:33,115
[SPEAKER_04]: They're gonna give out coats, they're gonna have information on fuel assistance, stuff like that.

61
00:04:33,795 --> 00:04:47,120
[SPEAKER_04]: But they did say that if my table, my table, my office or committees wanted to have a table and promote stuff or provide them with literature to hand out on anything, they were,

