67
00:05:05,100 --> 00:05:06,940
[SPEAKER_04]: holiday party, maybe?

68
00:05:07,441 --> 00:05:11,121
[SPEAKER_04]: I'd have to look up what the phrasing is this year.

69
00:05:12,482 --> 00:05:17,043
[SPEAKER_04]: It is the Wednesday after Thanksgiving, as usual.

70
00:05:17,703 --> 00:05:23,364
[SPEAKER_04]: And that is actually a really good, oh, it's called a winter extravaganza, and it's five to seven.

71
00:05:24,224 --> 00:05:30,506
[SPEAKER_04]: And that is actually a really good time to do outreach about things like climate change,

72
00:05:31,947 --> 00:05:36,830
[SPEAKER_04]: when it tends to be sort of a different population than goes to the Energy Festival.

73
00:05:37,470 --> 00:05:44,154
