75
00:05:48,937 --> 00:05:59,143
[SPEAKER_04]: It really attracts a lot of people who have lived in Medford their whole lives and go to the things that they know happen at a certain date and time every year.

76
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,001
[SPEAKER_04]: And this is one of those things.

77
00:06:01,982 --> 00:06:03,322
