254
00:20:31,993 --> 00:20:33,294
[SPEAKER_06]: Thought it was great.

255
00:20:33,794 --> 00:20:34,854
[SPEAKER_10]: I did send out an email.

256
00:20:34,894 --> 00:20:35,375
[SPEAKER_10]: Sorry, Lou.

257
00:20:36,155 --> 00:20:37,336
[SPEAKER_10]: We talked at the same time.

258
00:20:37,736 --> 00:20:40,897
[SPEAKER_10]: I did send out an email with some suggestions and observations.

259
00:20:41,918 --> 00:20:46,480
[SPEAKER_10]: I think the email new service is working, except for Barry, who bounces.

260
00:20:47,361 --> 00:20:48,281
[SPEAKER_10]: So I sent it to Barry.

261
00:20:48,321 --> 00:20:51,583
[SPEAKER_10]: So I don't know if you had a chance, everyone, to read the notes.

262
00:20:52,783 --> 00:20:54,925
[SPEAKER_06]: I'm not sure I'm still bouncing, by the way.

263
00:20:55,525 --> 00:20:55,965
[SPEAKER_10]: You are.

264
00:20:56,245 --> 00:20:59,667
[SPEAKER_10]: I get the notification back that it didn't go through.

265
00:21:02,203 --> 00:21:04,123
[SPEAKER_10]: So I sent it to you separately.

266
00:21:04,143 --> 00:21:08,785
[SPEAKER_03]: So why don't you just summarize your, your email?

267
00:21:09,825 --> 00:21:11,245
[SPEAKER_10]: Well, I don't have it in front of me.

268
00:21:11,465 --> 00:21:19,867
[SPEAKER_10]: So, and it was long and I didn't want to take too much time because I have a full agenda, but I thought it went, excuse me, really well.

269
00:21:20,568 --> 00:21:26,649
[SPEAKER_10]: And excuse me, I did hear back from, um, help see regarding how much material was collected.

270
00:21:26,769 --> 00:21:27,909
[SPEAKER_10]: And it was 1,067 pounds of material.

271
00:21:31,579 --> 00:21:33,160
[SPEAKER_10]: which is huge amount.

272
00:21:34,121 --> 00:21:42,066
[SPEAKER_10]: And for the dehumidifiers, 97 were collected, which was equivalent to 2000, I think it was $2,067 in rebates to residents.

273
00:21:46,527 --> 00:21:56,337
[SPEAKER_10]: So that's quite large considering Mass Save came in so late, just literally a few weeks before the event.

274
00:21:56,697 --> 00:21:59,040
[SPEAKER_10]: That's quite a bit, 97 humidifiers.

275
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:00,922
[SPEAKER_10]: So I think we did a great job.

276
00:22:01,002 --> 00:22:05,927
[SPEAKER_10]: I'm also in collecting recyclable items.

277
00:22:07,298 --> 00:22:11,579
[SPEAKER_10]: And as far as on green team junk removal, they're going to get back to me.

278
00:22:11,760 --> 00:22:14,941
