00:32:13,493 --> 00:32:15,575
[SPEAKER_02]: I thought it was great to see so many people.

372
00:32:16,476 --> 00:32:22,381
[SPEAKER_02]: We were in a couple of different neighborhoods trick-or-treating, and there was a lot of people talking about that event.

