01:11:17,414 --> 01:11:19,516
[SPEAKER_07]: comments that they're going to submit.

780
01:11:20,577 --> 01:11:21,518
[SPEAKER_10]: Oh, they did it already.

781
01:11:21,818 --> 01:11:22,519
[SPEAKER_07]: Okay.

