01:14:35,385 --> 01:14:36,826
[SPEAKER_10]: back to the committee, right?

820
01:14:38,387 --> 01:14:52,435
[SPEAKER_03]: Yeah, I'd like to see what the Trees Medford committee is gonna have, but I think the next meeting we'll have to have a, it would be nice to have something before us to review as a consolidated set of comments.

821
