[SPEAKER_10]: There were many plans for zoning and recommendations.

901
01:23:17,376 --> 01:23:20,077
[SPEAKER_10]: Oh, the environmental report that the city came out with.

902
01:23:20,350 --> 01:23:22,191
[SPEAKER_10]: There's a title for it, I forgot the name.

903
01:23:22,531 --> 01:23:23,511
[SPEAKER_10]: It's a big booklet.

904
01:23:24,631 --> 01:23:26,332
[SPEAKER_04]: The Climate Action and Adaptation.

905
01:23:26,572 --> 01:23:28,393
[SPEAKER_10]: Right, yes, okay.

