1047
01:37:23,695 --> 01:37:53,037
[SPEAKER_02]: um you know native trees or or others that have some sort of historical significance um and is there any sort of um way to remove a tree and then plant another one in a in a similar area that's like some sort of ability to to do that without uh a prohibitive cost i think would be my two main questions but if the answer is just go read the documentation i'll go do that as well well an answer to your question

