1089
01:41:45,435 --> 01:41:58,184
[SPEAKER_02]: or homeowners, or renters, or really anyone, are in between getting a proper permit and having a significant cost versus removing a fast-growing tree that might impact their property.

1090
01:41:58,204 --> 01:42:00,106
[SPEAKER_02]: That's the only concern I have.

1091
01:42:00,126 --> 01:42:01,827
[SPEAKER_02]: So thank you for that answer.

1092
